{"type": "article", "id": 13103, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-06T06:59:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 8906, "name": "盆栽"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 5858, "name": "茶具"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155848CtOpPRLo7shxbyFU.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tRimini Rimini Bags by Marcella De Faveri &amp; Marta Foschi \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>八月是夏天，也是秋天，一进八月就觉得夏天好像快要过完了似的。你有没有想过怎样保存夏天的记忆呀？Marcella De Faveri 和 Marta Foschi 两位设计师这样做的：他们回收了所在的海滨城市的废弃的阳伞，经过简单的加工后，做成了一个个的书包，为吹了一个夏天海风的阳伞带来了新的活力，而书包的图案也因为阳伞图案的多样而充满各种奇妙的可能性。这是<a href=\"http://www.riminiriminibags.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114612PdCe5UfvG7qhBjwJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114613KTZQRM21sqCu4wcE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114613LdFRrpZog3nYJK2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114614QhblyMrDt6KiAwaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140725tlkGSVm5Od9YEIue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5195599\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114615vK6DJTu9H5jnQoI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49388753\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146157LJ2sc4B1qTgVRrE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tRound Square Teaware by Chun-Tso Liu\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自台湾设计师 Chun-Tso Liu 的一套作品，他试图打破传统的茶具繁琐的设计和华丽的外表，剥落不必要的元素，推出了这套极简的圆柱形茶具，他甚至让把手消失，只留下一小块凸起作为辅助手持茶杯的工具，或是茶包的固定。设计师 Chun-Tso Liu 工程师出身，后转型工业设计，一直专注于极简的设计，这是他的<a href=\"http://www.chuntso.com/\" target=\"_blank\">个人主页</a>，点击查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146166FmOYKxgbkoiLsMP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6775\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146168ZjmC3zcHBPtipOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114617GcVZ2yR7QXau8k6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114617SbAMgRTQfOryGuJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114617rqpBj3W5GVT0gbtR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tHifi by Symbol Audio\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>现在得了一种“看见长条状有两个眼睛的物体就觉得像大白”的病，你看这个音箱，是不是就很像？这是 Symbol Audio 推出的一款桌面音箱，它有一个优质的低音喇叭，并且 2.1 通道扬声器支持各种输入方式。同时，音箱配备蓝牙接收模块，可以与任何支持蓝牙的设备配合，进行播放。产品有四种配色：胡桃木，橡木，灰色，黑白色，可配合不同装修风格挑选适合的颜色。最后送上<a href=\"http://www.symbolaudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Symbol Audio 的官方主页</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114618ieNWrEXdaRSUb8o1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114618emiHsacpK5S2fPwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114619I9NVoQgDKskTjXi7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114619u1y0JqLOmYrVEjH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146209xJDdjQIAcNZi56M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tLatitude Collection 2015 by Julie Gaillard \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这套名为 “经纬” 的家具和它的名字一样横平竖直，其中的“经线”部分可以随意移动，从而营造出不同的空间，根据用户的意愿收纳物品。这一系列里面有咖啡桌，高脚桌，边桌等不同类型的桌子，配色主打黄色，绿色和蓝色，与木质材料配合，看上去清新自然。这是<a href=\"http://www.juliegaillard.com/mobilier-latitude/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114620OJadfSl3L5rexF0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114621nuG15I9AFEMSf8oO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114621fMSmZA5D8XiJtOIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146210osnLgiZa5EdvGTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146223RmpNZevUgTQFxKa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114622Fw1VzqounNbyxk4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114623ZRAcxM89L3702gsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114623s2GoMROa3gr68E5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114624AHwZFUmz5SvjM9Ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114624tDEluqcAiLzCyVB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tUrbanoasis by Andrea Mangone\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>意大利设计师 Andrea Mangone 推出了一个叫做 “Urbanoasis” 的盆栽系列。我们生活中盆栽很常见，但是制作得这么精致的还是蛮难得。整套产品包括一个花盆，种子，干土肥料，浇水罐，甚至还有铲子，耙子等农作用具。有了这些，我们似乎可以有模有样地在家里开一片小农田了。<a href=\"http://www.andreamangone.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114624w6Yu2qv10btZ3JzL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114625XAqo9DsmzFlyBKSh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146262tSnz39m7i0Bv6yU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021146260VLZPJKc2FTx3AUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114627i08lHbmvszMrCyjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114627ClBr4RpWaM6nPv89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114629cUOE4I7ArvYwRJxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114629kImhcxH9y5BRv1El.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114630BsGyjR0uAOmLklxH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114630xbwfRQpeUdY12i9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tBag by Murakami Haruki &amp; Porter\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>村上春树读者们，这里有个好消息。近日，村上春树和 Porter 联合推出了一款单肩包。之前他开设了一个和读者们互动的网站，名为“村上先生的所在”，引起了大家踊跃的参与。于是出版社精选了网站的 400 多个问答集结成册，在今年七月推出了《村上先生的所在》实体书籍，这个帆布包就是以书籍为主题设计的配套单品。包包的大小正好可以装进一本书，正面绣有书名外，背后印上了书中的插画。海军蓝色也看上去清新可人。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140725IHSVn49plGUawuyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114631kP6NqA8Me4rHxSgm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114631a3MHZRxCh1L9KQXF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}